{"tid":2403644,"cid":5,"subCid":11,"title":"青年被控企圖襲警及管有鉗 罪名不成立 官:片段不見被告動作 只見好多人揮動警棍","createTime":"2021-02-11T08:04:32.000Z","updateTime":"2021-02-12T02:58:05.000Z","uid":240362,"like":38,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":20,"replies":[{"pid":"b7ba02fc7dba536dbc0510738513dad791663b64","tid":2403644,"uid":240362,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-11T08:04:32.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://t.me/youarenotalonehk_live/13630\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ft.me%2Fyouarenotalonehk_live%2F13630&d=i0%2FHWd2N8RLCa1A1b4xPLKQEQZ%2FBMmOowG797g%2FgSDo%3D&h=f6d18223\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://t.me/youarenotalonehk_live/13630</a><br />\n<br />\n#九龍城裁判法院第七庭 <br />\n#張天雁裁判官 <br />\n#1027九龍城 #裁決<br />\n#襲警 #管有工具作非法用途<br />\n<br />\n林（20）<br />\n<br />\n控罪一：企圖襲警<br />\n控罪二：管有工具適合作非法用途並意圖作非法用途使用<br />\n<br />\n背景：於去年10月27日，被告被控在九龍城品蘭街與界限街交界企圖襲擊在正當執行職務的偵緝警員17781；以及同日同地管有一把鉗子，意圖作非法用途使用。（獨媒）<br />\n<br />\n速報：🥳🥳兩項罪名不成立🥳🥳<br />\n❌訟費申請被駁回❌"},{"pid":"70ed16281ce3d47c08d2422f3bdb0d493c05cb79","tid":2403644,"uid":240362,"like":7,"dislike":0,"score":7,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2021-02-11T08:04:45.000Z","msg":"便衣警員何天佑憶述，去年10月27日下午應當日遊行活動，由警車接載到九龍城一帶執行職務。他目睹當日下午近5時半，在界限街品蘭街交界已有40至50人集結，由於路面較窄警方和集結人士一度被困在路口。何續指，被告當時身穿黑衣，戴上黑色帽和面巾，向他揮動一支鐵筆3至4下，兩人相距只有半至一米，而涉案鐵筆有35厘米長。何及時反應後退一步避過襲擊，然後徒手捉著被告的右手將他制服。同日6時，被告被帶返警署後在其背包內找出一把鉗。<br />\n<br />\n辯方質疑，既然何警員對被告向他揮舞鐵筆印象深刻，為何他沒有紀錄他當時以「企圖襲警」罪拘捕被告，他解釋，因為他沒有受傷，故當時不認為這是要項。<br />\n<br />\n裁判官張天雁觀看由控方提供的案發新聞片段，由於場面混亂而且人數眾多，裁判官批評片段質素，而且控方沒有提供截圖，令法庭難以判斷被告和事主身分，直言無法從片段中看到被告揮動鐵筆，反而「淨係見倒好多人揮動警棍」。盤問下警員承認片段是拍攝不到被告揮動鐵筆的一瞬間，因為他們入鏡前被告已完成他的動作。"},{"pid":"e0d9416809d5f58a3788e0a1f48108bd8a579da7","tid":2403644,"uid":27122,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-02-11T08:06:05.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f06738b5a15648cd7df312d8ff5794eea233974e","tid":2403644,"uid":240362,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"e0d9416809d5f58a3788e0a1f48108bd8a579da7","tid":2403644,"uid":27122,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-02-11T08:06:05.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-02-11T08:07:06.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"76957c73adc8374883504184dc664e28c36c2400","tid":2403644,"uid":240362,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-11T08:11:23.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f91b546b860170302887afa20195f871127ff1cf","tid":2403644,"uid":304769,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-11T08:11:28.000Z","msg":"淫審處好快堆滿司法界菁英<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"acf6abdf058a0762b20cc1d4cba95b70c32b83ff","tid":2403644,"uid":184261,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"70ed16281ce3d47c08d2422f3bdb0d493c05cb79","tid":2403644,"uid":240362,"like":7,"dislike":0,"score":7,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2021-02-11T08:04:45.000Z","msg":"便衣警員何天佑憶述，去年10月27日下午應當日遊行活動，由警車接載到九龍城一帶執行職務。他目睹當日下午近5時半，在界限街品蘭街交界已有40至50人集結，由於路面較窄警方和集結人士一度被困在路口。何續指，被告當時身穿黑衣，戴上